Day 17: Coach, Don’t Manage!
🎓 "A Scrum Master is a coach, not a manager!"  
👉 Tip: Guide your team with questions that make them think. Coaches help teams find their own solutions.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
